<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_36_r1l3"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> / Vns iſt in landmanſweiſe fürkumen / vvie daʒ groſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_36_r1l4"><expan>ſamnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> in francken / vnd vmb den Odenvvalt / ſeẏ / Bıten vvir etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_36_r1l6">ob Jr dauon icht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> het / oder wiſʒt / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_36_r1l5">vnd </ab></add> vvo ſie das haupt hin </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_36_r1l8">keren <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr vns das an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> brief 
<add><ab facs="#facs_36_r1l7">bey dıſem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>pote<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> wiſſen lieſʒt / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> VVer </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_36_r1l9">
<del rend="strikethrough">abe </del> <expan>Alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vveiſheit das füglich ſeẏ / Erfürt Jr aber fürbaʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_36_r1l10">davon icht / das lieſʒt vns bey <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>pote<ex>n</ex></expan> vviſſen <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_36_r1l11">das lone gern auſʒrihten / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Marie <expan>Magdalen<ex>e</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_36_r1l12"><expan>winſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_36" id="18r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> uns ist in landmansweise fürkumen, wie daz
                        grosz <expan>samnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> in Francken und umb den Odenwalt sey.
                        Biten wir etc., ob ir davon icht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> het oder
                        wiszt <add>und</add> wo sie das haupt hin keren
                            <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz ir uns das an
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> brief <add>bey disem
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>pote<ex>n</ex></expan></add> wissen lieszt,
                                <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weisheit das füglich sey. Erfürt ir aber
                        fürbaz davon icht, das lieszt uns bey <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>pote<ex>n</ex></expan> wissen, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir das lone gern auszrihten.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> marie
                                <expan>Magdalen<ex>e</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>Winsh<ex>eim</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>. </ab>
</div>
